75
00:04:20.260 --> 00:04:24.160
whose images are taken and stored do not offend in the next 12

76
00:04:24.220 --> 00:04:28.160
months, that data is deleted, and that's what we believe

77
00:04:28.200 --> 00:04:30.740
should happen in New Zealand.

78
00:04:32.080 --> 00:04:35.860
We could outline this in much greater detail, but to be

79
00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:36.540
truthful,

80
00:04:37.540 --> 00:04:41.230
the parliamentary committee, the Justice Committee, and you

81
00:04:41.340 --> 00:04:45.260
guys generally, have much more efficient and

82
00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:49.060
capable research people who can find this information.

83
