95
00:05:31.100 --> 00:05:35.020
If those people do not offend for the next 12 months, then that data

96
00:05:35.080 --> 00:05:37.240
should be deleted. That makes sense.

97
00:05:38.400 --> 00:05:42.320
There needs to be a clear purpose for why police are taking photos

98
00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:42.940
of someone

99
