purpose. Otherwise, effectively,

101
00:05:50.900 --> 00:05:54.580
anyone's photo can be taken by the police indiscriminately and

102
00:05:54.680 --> 00:05:58.200
stored forever. We believe this not to

103
00:05:58.240 --> 00:06:02.050
be a fair and reasonable situation, and we want

104
00:06:02.080 --> 00:06:04.662
it to be controlled.Um-

105
